Bioclipse Software Development Kit
----------------------------------

This Git repository holds the plugins for Eclipse (not Bioclipse) to help people
development new plugins for Bioclipse.

Reading material
----------------

New Project Wizard:

* http://help.eclipse.org/ganymede/index.jsp?topic=/org.eclipse.jdt.doc.isv/guide/jdt_api_wizards.htm

Requirements
------------

* Eclipse 3.5
* the JDT plugin
* the PDE plugin

How to test the Plugin
----------------------

1. open the net.bioclipse.sdk/plugin.xml
2. click the link 'Launch an Eclipse application'

How to build the Update Site
----------------------------

1. open the net.bioclipse.sdk_updateSite/site.xml
2. run 'Build All'

How to install the plugin
-------------------------

1. in Eclipse, do: Help -> Software Updates
2. choose the tab 'Available Software' and click the 'Add site...' button
3. pick 'Local...' and select the net.bioclipse.sdk_updateSite/ folder

